ays, we\u2019d love to hear what you think about all of the changes above \u2013 so head over to Facebook or Twitter to let us know!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>See you on the battlefield.<br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Titans! Update 1.28 is now available to download \u2013 here\u2019s what you can expect: Changes Infiltrators and Berserkers will no longer exit their Charge state&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=37"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":79,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37\/revisions\/79"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=37"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=37"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/blog.dawnoftitans.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=37"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}